<document
    xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/XDOC/2.0"
    xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
    xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/XDOC/2.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/xdoc-2.0.xsd">
    <properties>
        <title>Administration</title>
        <author
            email="rsb.development@openanalytics.eu">RSB Development</author>
    </properties>
    <body>
        <section name="JMX">
            <subsection name="RMI">
              <p>RSB exposes MBeans accessible with JMX locally and over RMI.</p>
              <p>By default, the remote process URI is: <b>service:jmx:rmi://127.0.0.1:9098/jndi/rmi://localhost:9099/myconnector</b></p>
            </subsection>
            <subsection name="HTTP">
              <p>All the MBeans are also accessible over HTTP</p>
              <p>By default, the (browsable) HTTP URL is: <b>http://localhost:8889</b></p>
            </subsection>
        </section>
    </body>
</document>